msgstr ""

#: src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1061 src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1155
msgid ""
"`cargo update --update-rust-version` (e.g. when updating minor version) "
"though this is dependent on what you dependencies are using for an MSRV"
