#: src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1062 src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1094
#: src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1125 src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1156
msgid ""
"✅ Packages can more easily offer unofficial support for an MSRV due to "
"shifting the building with MSRV-incompatible dependencies from an error to a "
