msgid ""
"Instead of adding `resolver = \"3\"`, we could keep the default resolver the "
"same as today but allow opt-in to MSRV-aware resolver via "
"`CARGO_RESOLVER_PRECEDENCE=rust-version`."
msgstr ""

#: src/3537-msrv-resolver.md:1077
msgid ""
"When building with old Rust versions, error messages could suggest re-"
